2054.subject: BIO
2054.descrlong: Explores the interrelationships among marine and estuarine organisms, and between the organisms and their environment. The seminar course emphasizes reading, critiquing, and synthesizing current and recent marine ecology publications describing ecological relationships from a broad range of marine environments. (Offered spring semester of odd years.)
